body:
I try download and  resize a remote image with format WEBP, but i found this issue

```ruby

            using (var httpClient = new HttpClient())
            using (var stream = await httpClient.GetStreamAsync(new Uri("http://www.gstatic.com/webp/gallery/2.webp")))
            using (var skBitmap = SKBitmap.Decode(stream))
            using (var destinationFile = new FileStream("D:/desktop/teste_webp_format.jpg", FileMode.OpenOrCreate))
            using (var resized = skBitmap.Resize(new SKImageInfo(100, 100), SKBitmapResizeMethod.Lanczos3))
            using (var image = SKImage.FromBitmap(resized))image.Encode(SKEncodedImageFormat.Jpeg, 100).SaveTo(destinationFile);
```

working fine with other image formats.

```ruby

            using (var httpClient = new HttpClient())
            using (var stream = await httpClient.GetStreamAsync(new Uri("https://www.gstatic.com/webp/gallery/4.sm.jpg")))
            using (var skBitmap = SKBitmap.Decode(stream))
            using (var destinationFile = new FileStream("D:/desktop/test_jpg_format.jpg", FileMode.OpenOrCreate))
            using (var resized = skBitmap.Resize(new SKImageInfo(100, 100), SKBitmapResizeMethod.Lanczos3))
            using (var image = SKImage.FromBitmap(resized)) image.Encode(SKEncodedImageFormat.Jpeg, 100).SaveTo(destinationFile);```
